snippet.title: Game Boy Color - Hello Kitty's Cube Frenzy © 1999 NewKidCo - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Help Hello Kitty find her way back from a puzzling dream world of fasting candy-colored cubes that could trap her in paradise forever! Falling cubes become building blocks that help Hello Kitty climb to collect prices and earn extra playing time. 11 levels of game play plus a bonus round interwoven with all new stories about Hello Kitty and super cute illustrations never seen before. 3 ways to play: single player with a friend in cooperation or head to head.
